headline: TE Connectivity (TEL) Declares Regular US$0.71 Dividend for December 2025
summary: TE Connectivity (TEL) recently affirmed a regular quarterly dividend, distributing $0.71 per share, which may have been a factor in its share price rising by nearly 27% last quarter. The company's strategic actions, such as a significant buyback tranche and positive earnings announcements, likely added weight to this rise in its stock price.
